                    "body": "PHP 5.3.8",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=chriskl",
                        "name": "chriskl",
                        "displayName": "Chris Kings-Lynne",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-08-30T03:17:09.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-08-30T03:17:09.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/51780",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=chriskl",
                        "name": "chriskl",
                        "displayName": "Chris Kings-Lynne",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Guys, this was broken in this exact commit, for 1.11:\r\n\r\nhttp:\/\/framework.zend.com\/code\/diff.php?repname=Zend+Framework&path=%2Fbranches%2Frelease-1.11%2Flibrary%2FZend%2FSoap%2FServer.php&\r\n\r\nSurely this is critical!?!?\r\n\r\nThe code is assuming that going 'echo SoapFault object' is the same as going 'SoapServer->fault()' - which it is not!",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=chriskl",
                        "name": "chriskl",
                        "displayName": "Chris Kings-Lynne",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-09-03T05:45:03.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-09-03T05:45:03.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/52207",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=exander",
                        "name": "exander",
                        "displayName": "Alexander Weps",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Patch for this issue?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=exander",
                        "name": "exander",
                        "displayName": "Alexander Weps",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-11-07T18:51:35.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-11-07T18:51:35.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/52227",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=grummfy",
                        "name": "grummfy",
                        "displayName": "Van Belle Jonathan",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Hello,\r\nto make a quick fix i do this :\r\nin Zend_Soap_Server, around line 899 I change this :\r\n{code}\r\n        if ($fault) {\r\n            $this->_response = $fault;\r\n        }\r\n{code}\r\nto this \r\n{code}\r\n        if ($fault) {\r\n        \t$soap->fault($fault->faultcode, $fault->faultstring);\r\n        }\r\n{code}\r\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=grummfy",
                        "name": "grummfy",
                        "displayName": "Van Belle Jonathan",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-11-08T14:30:52.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-11-08T14:30:52.000+0000"
                },
